===============================================================================
Preliminary notes:
------------------
Mark "o": new feature
Mark "*": bug fixed.
Mark "!": change that can break compatibility with older version
===============================================================================

version 1.7.4, 2021/02/27
=========================
o Updated nehan(v7.6.1 -> v7.6.3).
o Fixed anchor preview position depending on the block location.
o Added math tag(syntax: <math>c = $pm$sqrt{ a^2 + b^2 }</math>, <math class="inline">sin$theta</math>).
o Added code highlight(syntax: <pre><code class="lang-xxx">...</code></pre>).

